-- Banco Popolare May Eliminate 800 Jobs Over Next Two Years, Il Sole Reports
-- B y   C h i a r a   R e m o n d i n i
-- 2010-10-08T05:42:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-08/banco-popolare-may-eliminate-800-jobs-over-next-two-years-il-sole-reports.html
Banco Popolare SC may cut about 800
jobs this year and next as it seeks to reduce costs, daily Il
Sole 24 Ore reported today.  Banco Popolare presented the proposal to labor unions in a
preview of its plan, which includes 300 reductions this year and
500 in 2011, Sole said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chiara Remondini at 
 cremondini@bloomberg.net  